modShortDescription: This mod removes all custom waypoints from the compass, they appear only on the map. All the other waypoints remain on the compass.
modDescription:
This mod removes all custom waypoints from the compass, they appear only on the map. All the other waypoints; mission waypoints, quick waypoint, land claim, vehicles, turrets etc. remain on the compass.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/Androthi/7D2D-Modlets/tree/main/AND-DeclutterCompass)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/24186-declutter-compass-modlet/).
